export default function CreatePerson() {
  return (
    <form>
      <fieldset>
        <label htmlFor="name">
          Name
          <input required type="text" id="name" placeholder="Name" />
        </label>
        <label htmlFor="email">
          Email <input required type="email" placeholder="Email address" />
        </label>
        <label htmlFor="number">
          Phone Number <input type="number" placeholder="phone number" />
        </label>
      </fieldset>
    </form>
  );
}
